bugtrap03.bugdomain.usersystem

Class User

  • java.lang.Object
    • bugtrap03.bugdomain.usersystem.User
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    Administrator, Issuer

    public abstract class User
extends java.lang.Object
    A User can be identified by his/her username. The uniqueness of this username is guaranteed by checking with all other ever created Users.
    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
